### PoFunQuiz API Debugging (.http file)
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or Visual Studio .http support

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

### Health Check — verify all connections to APIs and databases
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Diagnostics — exposes masked connection strings, keys, settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/diag
Accept: application/json

###

### Generate Quiz Questions (General Knowledge)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/questions?count=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Generate Quiz Questions (specific category)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/questions?count=5&category=Science
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Leaderboard (General category)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard?category=General
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit a Leaderboard Score
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "TST",
  "score": 42,
  "maxStreak": 3,
  "category": "General",
  "datePlayed": "2026-02-07T00:00:00Z",
  "wins": 1,
  "losses": 0
}

###

### OpenAPI Spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Scalar API Reference UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1
